ğŸ’¡ Notes:

Many early city-states like Lagash, Uruk, and Kish had periods of dominance, but they were usually smaller than what we consider â€œempires.â€

Some historians include Elamite expansions in southern Iran or Hurrian-Mittani rule as Mesopotamian-era empires.

